\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Per-circuit $\Delta v$ (\% violations) and $\Delta h$ (\% HPWL, macros-only) for VSR-post at $\lambda {=}2$ and $\lambda {=}8$ (the operator family) plus the four primary baselines, mean $\pm $std over 4 seeds. Negative is improvement. At fixed $\lambda {=}2$ VSR-post trades minimum HPWL inflation for moderate legality gain; at $\lambda {=}8$ it trades equivalent legality for substantially better HPWL. cg-strong and RePaint-binary are in the supplement.}}{5}{table.caption.21}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{tab:main}{{1}{5}{Per-circuit $\Delta v$ (\% violations) and $\Delta h$ (\% HPWL, macros-only) for VSR-post at $\lambda {=}2$ and $\lambda {=}8$ (the operator family) plus the four primary baselines, mean $\pm $std over 4 seeds. Negative is improvement. At fixed $\lambda {=}2$ VSR-post trades minimum HPWL inflation for moderate legality gain; at $\lambda {=}8$ it trades equivalent legality for substantially better HPWL. cg-strong and RePaint-binary are in the supplement}{table.caption.21}{}}
