\newlabel{fig:lambda_sweep}{{3}{7}{$\lambda $-sweep on 6 circuits (3 seeds, errorbars $=$ std). Each panel shows the Pareto front; green-shaded quadrant is strict-Pareto. Increasing $\lambda $ moves operating points leftward (lower HPWL) at near-constant violation reduction}{figure.caption.30}{}}
